{"tid":132551,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"2016 意大利之旅","createTime":"2017-02-24T02:10:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T04:03:20.000Z","uid":12599,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e5b4eaa6daf773725de93ca307bd24a13966f3b7","tid":132551,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T02:10:49.000Z","msg":"去年二月去完了日本後就一直沒有更新Blog,主要原因是...因為懶。其實這半年來出動拍攝的次數還是不少的,但每次都是拍攝處理完後就放上了Flickr或是Facebook了事。九月有個小假期就跟兩位朋友去了意大利玩了十天。很可惜整個旅程都是陰晴不定,拍出來的照片還達不到心中理想的程度。今次遊記還是簡單地用攝影作記錄就好。<br />\n<br />\n這次意大利之旅主要目的城市為羅馬,威尼斯,佛羅倫斯和拿不勒斯周邊地區。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/9/8143/29225984613_0c6b51630c_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F9%2F8143%2F29225984613_0c6b51630c_b.jpg&h=bad9d70f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為錢不多的關係,只能乘搭中國國際航空在北京轉機。當日北京的天氣還是不錯的。<br />\n<br />\n搭了十多個鐘頭飛機抵達羅馬已經是夜深,在羅馬休息一晚後便出發前往拿不勒斯。其實在拿不勒斯市內是沒有計劃任何行程的,第一站的目的地是距離拿不勒斯大約一小時鐵路路程的龐貝古城。<br />\n<br />\n早前在香港參觀過一個龐貝古城的展覽,大概了解當時龐貝為羅馬附近的一個重要港口城市。在公元79年龐貝後方的維蘇威火山爆發,整座城市一夜被毀。一直到18世紀,才被歷史學家重新發掘出來。由於被火山灰掩埋了大部城的城市,整個古城還保存著完好的外貌,有好一部份的建築保存完整,地上及牆上的畫作顏料清晰可見。有趣的是,在19世紀的挖掘發現了不少空洞內有人和動物的骸骨。這些小洞是由於火山灰掩埋了當時未能離開的居民,加上屍體的肉腐爛後留下骨頭和人形軀殼。考古學家將石膏灌入這這洞中做成鑄像，記錄下當時龐貝的狀況,令龐貝聞名於世。。這些石膏像雖在香港的博物館已看過一次,但在現場再看一次,還是很震撼的畫面。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/8/7581/29816985566_a4a8b6f035_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F8%2F7581%2F29816985566_a4a8b6f035_b.jpg&h=f5667891&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n龐貝古城的入口處。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/9/8358/29852312235_f10e2f7b8d_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F9%2F8358%2F29852312235_f10e2f7b8d_b.jpg&h=013588de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n龐貝古城中加入了不少現代的藝術作品。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5467/29816954726_8e5ccf008a_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5467%2F29816954726_8e5ccf008a_b.jpg&h=c31eecdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5768/29769501371_603573efc3_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5768%2F29769501371_603573efc3_b.jpg&h=590e5ad9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/9/8144/29769365491_aa2c64fb31_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F9%2F8144%2F29769365491_aa2c64fb31_b.jpg&h=d36b403c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n龐貝古城的一角。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/9/8435/29559008980_75c4430cdb_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F9%2F8435%2F29559008980_75c4430cdb_b.jpg&h=71235505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n龐貝除了古城外,新城區還有一座數百年歷史的教堂。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/9/8688/29816705376_78ea6ac47e_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F9%2F8688%2F29816705376_78ea6ac47e_b.jpg&h=f859e24f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n龐貝市的火車站,是環維蘇威鐵路的其中一站。<br />\n(待續...)<br />\n<br />\nBlogger: <a href=\"http://optikahk.blogspot.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foptikahk.blogspot.hk%2F&d=Xx1rX%2BBWBBKZa4OSQyufSf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=f5a146da\" target=\"_blank\">http://optikahk.blogspot.hk/</a><br />\nFlickr: <a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/40709744@N06/albums\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flickr.com%2Fphotos%2F40709744%40N06%2Falbums&d=Xx1rX%2BBWBBKZa4OSQyufSf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=74d1bf90\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.flickr.com/photos/40709744@N06/albums</a><br />\nFacebook Page: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Optika-%E5%85%89%E5%AD%B8%E8%AA%8C-393095131066228/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FOptika-%25E5%2585%2589%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E8%25AA%258C-393095131066228%2F&d=Xx1rX%2BBWBBKZa4OSQyufSf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=db61a8ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Optika-%E5%85%89%E5%AD%B8%E8%AA%8C-393095131066228/</a>"},{"pid":"8aced1e1c06259e60fed8711b224dcb8e04ba853","tid":132551,"uid":58911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T02:19:50.000Z","msg":"圖好靚 留名"},{"pid":"03e6036eeb97c2d1599fd2313c26183caa19a07b","tid":132551,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T02:23:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>圖好靚 留名</blockquote><br />\n多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96ca56be27f8d2c4b0e8f9a2f64cce81489201fe","tid":132551,"uid":44377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T02:34:55.000Z","msg":"感覺好似睇過<br />\nanyway留名等睇靚相"},{"pid":"b3d9f0c6c1292be3425ff8336a8a1231f6fcf745","tid":132551,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T14:49:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42b0fc38acaf0b81a1b4cbf59912a173f9e3164c","tid":132551,"uid":12599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T04:27:20.000Z","msg":"義大利之旅第二站是那不勒斯市近郊的Amalfi Coast地區。此一區好比香港的南區及離島的混<br />\r\n合體,有非常優美的海岸線及有特色的南意大利小城。<br />\r\n要前往Amalfi Coast地區,可在在那不勒斯火車站乘搭環維蘇威鐵路(也就是往龐培古城的同一<br />\r\n線路)先前往Sorrento。這一區是著名的檸檬產地,但檸檬的品種不是我們常見的新奇士種,體積<br />\r\n比拳頭還要大,主要用作製造Lemon Cello(檸檬甜酒)。Sorrento最著名的手信就是這種很甜的<br />\r\n烈酒,濃度可達30-40%,一般意大利人會作餐後酒用。不過要Lemon Cello作手信不用在這裡買,<br />\r\n可以到羅馬的超市酒品部,性價比會較遊客區好很多。<br />\r\n作為著名的南意渡假區,其實選擇住在Sorrento會比那不勒斯要好很多。那不勒斯是意大利著<br />\r\n名的罪惡之城,景點也不是太多,反而Sorrento南可達Amalfi Coast, 北有龐培,東邊則有Salerno<br />\r\n。如果打算到南意的海岸渡假,Sorrento會是一個比那不勒斯更佳的選擇。<br />\r\nSorrento附近有兩個比較風景漂亮的區域,一是Almalfi,另一是Positano。在Sorrento跟Salerno<br />\r\n都有巴士可以抵達,不過要等很久才有車,每車都是塞爆的,出發前一定要預留充足時間等車。<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5729/29613940690_2dc1b0619f_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5729%2F29613940690_2dc1b0619f_b.jpg&h=5f3b7d0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n當日先到Amalfi,但當日在下雨,拍出來能見人的只有一張相。<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/8/7546/29873165146_7a5895de23_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F8%2F7546%2F29873165146_7a5895de23_b.jpg&h=80109fba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n下午前往Positano,中途天氣轉晴,非常優美的風景。<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5677/29281868903_4367debd93_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5677%2F29281868903_4367debd93_b.jpg&h=cafb62bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n依山而建的彩色小屋。<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5137/29613912300_578a1c182b_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5137%2F29613912300_578a1c182b_b.jpg&h=d2218b9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n我們在巴士線中途下車,沿著車路近賞Positano的風景。<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/9/8049/29794192492_d009d68c97_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F9%2F8049%2F29794192492_d009d68c97_b.jpg&h=09ff120c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/9/8435/29280827074_81b45e2e59_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F9%2F8435%2F29280827074_81b45e2e59_b.jpg&h=88737b6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/9/8539/29824959411_1aa70a7bee_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F9%2F8539%2F29824959411_1aa70a7bee_b.jpg&h=eb526611&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/9/8539/29280803494_182f05f418_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F9%2F8539%2F29280803494_182f05f418_b.jpg&h=c4987937&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n(待續...)"},{"pid":"a4bf5078167eba5ef209daf3b1ff5fb4b59e4b99","tid":132551,"uid":563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T04:40:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2b37c89bb793d2c8f1015b51424100e8a93f0f8","tid":132551,"uid":11603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T08:59:29.000Z","msg":"LM 支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a3e3d6a0c7f76a1e7dd5e54f96d53dbf7bc6519","tid":132551,"uid":25512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T09:05:24.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"2db4651b42d87471f0e4b87b017f5d819bd31295","tid":132551,"uid":47565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T09:31:33.000Z","msg":"Positano靚過amalfi 好多<br />\n個陣行完上網睇番啲相先發覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n南意個種風情真係好想去多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有Naples 好多好西食，不過個陣獨遊緊，淆底地路過左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a5e926bad9d7e2882a81b29d8aada31aa55694","tid":132551,"uid":80909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T10:01:19.000Z","msg":"圖好靚<br />\n好奇一問 用咩filter<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd1c04ba88053cf034df100506cf98803152093e","tid":132551,"uid":73311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T12:25:18.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"6d155a7cc88f499c0382123994e153b4f2dc958f","tid":132551,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T06:21:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>圖好靚<br />\n好奇一問 用咩filter<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用lightroom 套VSCO再自己較色"},{"pid":"87b5cd9432e149bdd26f7455f3e044ab490f2063","tid":132551,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T06:22:32.000Z","msg":"離開那不勒斯,下一站是著名的水城威尼斯。<br />\n<br />\n這一站拍到很多相,但回到家中發現相片都非常的「遊客」。果然,要拍出好相片,事前的準備是非常重要的。<br />\n<br />\n威尼斯是個很有風情的古城,很可惜,今次旅程拍不出太合心水的人文照片。朋友提議去運河看日出,雖然辛苦了一點但還是有點例景相可以交功課...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/9/8020/29910271816_c9ced27dbc_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F9%2F8020%2F29910271816_c9ced27dbc_b.jpg&h=f89fe83f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聖馬可廣場日落<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/9/8413/29318016153_b1b1ea5bda_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F9%2F8413%2F29318016153_b1b1ea5bda_b.jpg&h=33c9ab54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPonte di Rialto 橋的大運河夜景<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5569/29317960203_a63f4dd65c_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5569%2F29317960203_a63f4dd65c_b.jpg&h=e9f01bc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPonte dell'Accademia 橋可以看到日出,這時間船很少,遊客也不多<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5565/29317288704_0cacc37c77_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5565%2F29317288704_0cacc37c77_b.jpg&h=2cefdfbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黎明時份的安康聖母聖殿<br />\n(待續...)"},{"pid":"a12e56ee533643c8e90b49cc23203ec28737c5bb","tid":132551,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T06:27:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Positano靚過amalfi 好多<br />\n個陣行完上網睇番啲相先發覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n南意個種風情真係好想去多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有Naples 好多好西食，不過個陣獨遊緊，淆底地路過左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nPositano真係正好多,但好多tour都唔知點解話去amalfi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78a9d26a1c98c94a0dabf1835e66b93b090388d2","tid":132551,"uid":80893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T10:50:07.000Z","msg":"影得好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"059603dcd3806de54d4f50bdb3947c7f130b1083","tid":132551,"uid":67779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T08:27:57.000Z","msg":"文呢??"},{"pid":"a54382324153f4be397c0ea2169fb041c4d947f7","tid":132551,"uid":17166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T09:25:00.000Z","msg":"留明<br />\n等睇羅馬"},{"pid":"64f7b4f406e8f988be3b01e6f22a7d067892dbbe","tid":132551,"uid":43051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T09:29:00.000Z","msg":"威尼斯污糟過大陸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c72d6940a5a4523538cbdc86160344c13f8799bd","tid":132551,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T12:58:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>威尼斯污糟過大陸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你去過未架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50c0489505bd0403e56be4f7e20a736423589724","tid":132551,"uid":11525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T13:22:52.000Z","msg":"留名睇靚相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e65d2a8e5b4ffbefbc99df932a1f9224bac2a03f","tid":132551,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T13:27:04.000Z","msg":"由拿不勒斯直接去威尼斯？"},{"pid":"30eb3b85d4074ec1a712446be39f7ef1be0a052f","tid":132551,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T01:55:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由拿不勒斯直接去威尼斯？</blockquote><br />\n我買左rail pass,時間唔夠唯有咁行,一早火車去"},{"pid":"5623b8ab0cd57ec8531a78dedb0bf3faefc06f1a","tid":132551,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T01:57:25.000Z","msg":"繼續威尼斯旅行的相片...<br />\n<br />\n作為文藝復興時期義大利東北方的重要商港,威尼斯除本島外還有不少周圍小島,主要是作工業生產。當中比較有名的有玻璃島Murano及彩色島Burano。不過由本島前往外島的船票都不便宜,加上時間的問題只前往了Burano。<br />\n<br />\n在Ponte dell'Accademia 橋看完日出後前往斯拉夫人堤岸。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/9/8093/29360076334_a85180833c_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F9%2F8093%2F29360076334_a85180833c_b.jpg&h=5321fd9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聖馬可廣場總督宮,日出的光芒在廊柱間射出,配合魚肚白的天空,不錯的景色。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/9/8469/29874177582_f4c131f232_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F9%2F8469%2F29874177582_f4c131f232_b.jpg&h=8a835539&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n提拉夫人堤岸,貢多拉在日出的光照下被曬成金黃色。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/9/8418/29360032644_c296db9e94_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F9%2F8418%2F29360032644_c296db9e94_b.jpg&h=cb0942c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日出時份的貢多拉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/9/8140/29874132322_d902daf817_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F9%2F8140%2F29874132322_d902daf817_b.jpg&h=6668eed8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/9/8369/29904281591_2945600ab3_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F9%2F8369%2F29904281591_2945600ab3_b.jpg&h=c20eab78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n長曝一張。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5520/29904268321_f033635a91_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5520%2F29904268321_f033635a91_b.jpg&h=e88e5c66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聖喬治馬焦雷島,沒有時間過去參觀。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/9/8498/29359950094_818044240e_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F9%2F8498%2F29359950094_818044240e_b.jpg&h=73bea205&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 維托里奧&middot;埃馬努埃萊二世紀念像。他好像是威尼斯人,後來成為統一義大利全境的君主。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5592/29360993293_d2279529f3_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5592%2F29360993293_d2279529f3_b.jpg&h=0d10f806&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n彩色島Burano。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/9/8665/29359944564_d87de6d205_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F9%2F8665%2F29359944564_d87de6d205_b.jpg&h=88dae4fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n趁早過來沒有遊客,很舒服。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/9/8103/29953633956_7b255a292c_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F9%2F8103%2F29953633956_7b255a292c_b.jpg&h=2fefc2f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(待續...)"},{"pid":"cc6864fbf37abc6f0d6488ae895ef8601389d67b","tid":132551,"uid":24532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T02:17:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>繼續威尼斯旅行的相片...<br />\n<br />\n作為文藝復興時期義大利東北方的重要商港,威尼斯除本島外還有不少周圍小島,主要是作工業生產。當中比較有名的有玻璃島Murano及彩色島Burano。不過由本島前往外島的船票都不便宜,加上時間的問題只前往了Burano。<br />\n<br />\n在Ponte dell'Accademia 橋看完日出後前往斯拉夫人堤岸。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/9/8093/29360076334_a85180833c_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F9%2F8093%2F29360076334_a85180833c_b.jpg&h=5321fd9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聖馬可廣場總督宮,日出的光芒在廊柱間射出,配合魚肚白的天空,不錯的景色。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/9/8469/29874177582_f4c131f232_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F9%2F8469%2F29874177582_f4c131f232_b.jpg&h=8a835539&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n提拉夫人堤岸,貢多拉在日出的光照下被曬成金黃色。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/9/8418/29360032644_c296db9e94_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F9%2F8418%2F29360032644_c296db9e94_b.jpg&h=cb0942c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日出時份的貢多拉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/9/8140/29874132322_d902daf817_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F9%2F8140%2F29874132322_d902daf817_b.jpg&h=6668eed8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/9/8369/29904281591_2945600ab3_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F9%2F8369%2F29904281591_2945600ab3_b.jpg&h=c20eab78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n長曝一張。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5520/29904268321_f033635a91_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5520%2F29904268321_f033635a91_b.jpg&h=e88e5c66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聖喬治馬焦雷島,沒有時間過去參觀。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/9/8498/29359950094_818044240e_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F9%2F8498%2F29359950094_818044240e_b.jpg&h=73bea205&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 維托里奧&middot;埃馬努埃萊二世紀念像。他好像是威尼斯人,後來成為統一義大利全境的君主。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5592/29360993293_d2279529f3_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5592%2F29360993293_d2279529f3_b.jpg&h=0d10f806&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n彩色島Burano。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/9/8665/29359944564_d87de6d205_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F9%2F8665%2F29359944564_d87de6d205_b.jpg&h=88dae4fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n趁早過來沒有遊客,很舒服。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/9/8103/29953633956_7b255a292c_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F9%2F8103%2F29953633956_7b255a292c_b.jpg&h=2fefc2f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(待續...)</blockquote><br />\n巴打d相好靚，意大利我剩係去過羅馬"}]}